General.Name: Terranet AB
General.Description: Terranet AB designs and develops sensor applications for road safety. It offers BlincVision that combines laser scanning, event cameras, and advanced vision software to generate real time 4D images of road object. It serves vehicle manufacturing, subcontractors, and other players in transportation and mobility sector. The company was formerly known as TerraNet Holding AB (publ). The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
